## 4. API Routes

### Auth  `POST /api/auth/`

| Method | Path | Auth | Description |
|--------|------|------|-------------|
| POST | `/register` | No | Register with name, email, password |
| POST | `/login` | No | Login, returns JWT |
| POST | `/firebase-login` | No | Verify Firebase idToken, return app JWT |

### Products  `GET /api/products`

| Method | Path | Auth | Description |
|--------|------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/` | No | Return all products |

### Orders  `/api/orders`

| Method | Path | Auth | Description |
|--------|------|------|-------------|
| POST | `/` | JWT | Place a new order |
| GET | `/` | JWT | Get logged-in retailer's orders |

