## 5. Auth Flow

```
Email/Password Registration & Login
в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
Client вҶ’ POST /api/auth/register вҶ’ bcrypt hash вҶ’ save User вҶ’ return JWT
Client вҶ’ POST /api/auth/login    вҶ’ verify hash вҶ’ return JWT

Google / Firebase Sign-In
в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
Client вҶ’ Firebase SDK вҶ’ Google Auth вҶ’ Firebase idToken
Client вҶ’ POST /api/auth/firebase-login { idToken }
Backend вҶ’ firebase-admin.verifyIdToken(idToken)
        вҶ’ find/create User by firebaseUid
        вҶ’ sign and return app JWT

Protected Route Access
в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
Client вҶ’ request with Authorization: Bearer <JWT>
Backend middleware вҶ’ jwt.verify(token, JWT_SECRET)
                  вҶ’ attach req.user = { userId }
                  вҶ’ next()
```

---

## 6. Technology Decisions

| Decision | Choice | Reason |
|----------|--------|--------|
| DB | MongoDB + Mongoose | Flexible schema, Atlas free tier |
| Auth | JWT (HS256) | Stateless, easy to verify on both web and mobile |
| Social auth | Firebase Admin SDK | Handles Google OAuth complexity; backend just verifies token |
| Web framework | Next.js | SSR for products page, file-based routing |
| Mobile | Expo + React Native | Fastest cross-platform setup for assessment |
| HTTP client | Axios | Interceptors for token injection |
| Token storage | localStorage (web), AsyncStorage (mobile) | Platform-appropriate |

---

## 7. Security Notes

- All passwords hashed with bcrypt (salt rounds вүҘ 10).
- JWT secret in `.env`, never committed.
- Firebase credentials in `.env`, never committed.
- `.env.example` shows keys without values.
- Orders API validates ownership вҖ” users can only see their own orders.